        .mission-body
            h2.mission-heading
                | Doomscrolling, binge-watching, compulsive checking — these aren't just bad habits.
                | They are patterns encoded in neural circuitry.
            p.mission-text
                | Most people understand addiction in abstract terms. They know it "affects the brain," but that abstraction makes it easy to dismiss — in others and in ourselves. This tool exists to close that gap: to turn data and research into something you can rotate, cross-section, and explore.
            p.mission-text
                | Whether you're a clinician, a student, or someone simply trying to understand your own habits, this tool gives you a shared visualization for conversations that matter.